data.title: Richard Mangum, superior court judge and Flagstaff Hikes author, dies at 81
data.meta_description: It’s difficult to measure a person’s love for their community, but it would be hard to find a man more devoted to Flagstaff’s present and past than Richard “Dick” Mangum.
